column2: Sample Identifier; single identifier for set of 3 Porites nubbins and 3 Montipora nubbins
Porites compressa or Montipora capitata
Initial Buoyant Weight (g) of 3 nubbins
Temperature (C) at time of initial buoyant weighing
Date of initial buoyant weighing
Final Buoyant Weight (g) of 3 nubbins
Temperature (C) at time of final buoyant weighing
Date of final buoyant weighing
Initial Dry Weight of coral set based on buoyant wt; calculated from InitialBW and InitialTemp based on Davies (1989) and a coral density of 2.93 g/cm3
Final Dry Weight of coral set based on buoyant wt; calculated from FinalBW and FinalTemp based on Davies (1989) and a coral density of 2.93 g/cm3
DeltaBW = FinalBWcorr - InitBWcorr; this is the change in dry weight over the 6 wk experiment based on buoyant weights
pcDeltaBW = DeltaBW/InitBWcorr; this is the percent change in dry weight based on buoyant weight
Total volume (cm3) of 3 nubbins based on displacement; from dataframe CoralNubb
Total surface area (cm2) of 3 nubbins based on displacement; summed from dataframe CoralNubb
Total ashed weight (g) of 3 nubbins based on displacement; summed from dataframe CoralNubb
Total dry weight (g) of 3 nubbins based on displacement; summed from dataframe CoralNubb
Total ash-free dry weight (g) of 3 nubbins based on displacement; summed from dataframe CoralNubb
AFDW/DW; organic matter as a percent of total dry weight
Nutrient level assigned to the aquarium: Ambient/Medium/High
Tank Identifier; each aquarium was assigned to one of 3 tanks
Aquarium Identifier for Experiment 1; nine aquaria held coral nubbins in expt 1
Aquarium Identifier for Experiment 2; all aquaria had coral nubbins in expt 2
Flag if measurement appears to be outlier
